location.fullValue: Sophie Plan, The Preserve at Gilbert Meadows

data.description: Welcome Home! This Gorgeous Barry Andrews built home is located in the sought after community of Seven Trails. Stone front Colonial style model,  offers a sitting room upon entry, a formal dining room,  hardwood floors throughout main level ( carpet in Family room), an open floor plan ,an impressive eat-in kitchen with stainless steel appliances, beautiful maple cabinetry and a double sink. The adjacent  family room features recessed lighting, gas fireplace and newer carpet. Sliders lead to a large deck with walk-down stairs to a fully fenced flat yard .The upper level boasts a 20 x 20  master suite with a cathedral ceiling, a massive walk in closet, laminate flooring and attached super bath - with a double vanity, soaking tub and separate shower. The additional bedrooms are roomy with new carpet and share a hall bathroom. The lower level has an additional 1300 sq ft of space-waiting for your personal touches.  Lovingly maintained by original owners, this could be your new Home Sweet Home! An oversized 2 car garage offers additional storage.   Call to schedule your private showing. Expected date on market 2/24
